Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穆罕默德·阿布德爾還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個壞消息…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要盡快通知迪奧和你的替身使者同伴對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 卡梅歐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要告訴他們 真的一定要告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴喬斯達先生 花京院 承太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是令人吃驚的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 消息的內容要這樣修改後再傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,審判卡梅歐不僅殺了波魯納雷夫那傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還順手將活著的阿布德爾幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 變成好消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色魔術師！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是個力量很強的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 他不僅有力量而且速度也快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德爾 你的力量不過如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來真能傳回去好消息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hail 2 U
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我的雪莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪莉…已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…只是個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波魯納雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我收回剛才說你沒有長進的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該道歉的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負已定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德爾 說出你的三個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來替你實現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次真的在你死之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 說來看看 三個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德爾 別理他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒必要說出願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德爾 你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 給我四個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是願望啊 願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的願望是把三個願望變成四個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘖嘖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙…開這種玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是拒絕嗎 卡梅歐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己提出的 必須遵守諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還想白費力氣比拚力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這腿踢得真是軟弱無力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘖嘖 第一個願望是讓你發出痛苦的叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 好強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比剛才厲害得多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被倒吊男刺中的背傷還沒完全治好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:14:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才因為要護著傷口 沒有使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天前在印度 我硬撐著才勉強站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這個島坐的是飛機 所以旅途還算輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是阿布德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 第二個願望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你發出恐懼的慘叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及第三個願望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後悔的哭聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混…混賬 他逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站住 畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓 安靜點 波魯納雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的力量與速度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身使者的真身必定在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是替身的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:14:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該藏在很近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真身就藏在這地下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 要怎麼對付他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我的妹妹也被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要讓你下地獄 Hell 2 U
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把各種東西塞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥土 沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛…螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有火柴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 還沒完沒完 沒完沒完 沒完沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 波魯納雷夫 感覺快憋不住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼久違的男子漢間的友情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一起就地解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘖嘖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…總算熬過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊 笑一個吧 波魯納雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑吧笑吧 波魯納雷夫 啊哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德爾 你的性格是不是變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前應該不會想出這種下流的點子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會因為腦袋被槍打壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊 來啊 瞄準一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請饒了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四個願望…那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不理會你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色魔術師不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘鏘
